\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 The Elephant in the Church\

\fs28 Week 1 - The Sex Elephant
\f1\b0 \

\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \
\
Talk about the analogy of the Elephant in the room\
\
\
Intro:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The church for years has been answering questions no one is asking and avoiding topics everyone is talking about\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This series is designed to walk through some of the major issues we are talking about and hopefully frame them in a way that points towards God\'92s standards because\'85I\'92ve heard it said before that when we break God\'92s standards it doesn\'92t break Him, it breaks us.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And right now we many people with sexual dysfunction and frustration.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf2 Now for the matters you wrote about: \'93It is good for a man not to have sexual relations with a woman.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(need to sit here and expound on this)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But since sexual immorality is occurring, each man should have sexual relations with his own wife, and each woman with her own husband.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is one of the causes when a couple tries to be spiritual or downplay their role in their marriage as it relates to sex?  Sexual Immorality!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Well I don\'92t have a husband yet or a wife yet\'85.then you don\'92t get to have sex!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe one of the reasons we live in a culture where adult men are like boys still is because one of biggest motivators to become an adult has been given away too freely!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The husband should fulfill his marital duty to his wife,\'a0and likewise the wife to her husband.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This might be the most important and least sexy verse in the Bible.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sex is a duty!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are your spouse\'92s only legitimate release of sexual expression.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The wife does not have authority over her own body but yields it to her husband. In the same way, the husband does not have authority over his own body but yields it to his wife.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul says your body is not your own.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People talk all the time about it is my body\'85not if you\'92re married it\'92s not.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You gave up that right\'85that individuality.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem today with so many marriage is that people love the idea of being with someone sexually and intimately and playing house but they don\'92t love the practicality of marriage.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Marriage takes work, sacrifice, and commitment to make work and at the end of the day you are not your own.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have entered into a covenant, willingly, to give of yourself for the rest of your life.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 5\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Do not deprive each other except perhaps by mutual consent and for a time,\'a0so that you may devote yourselves to prayer. \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Except perhaps\'85I love this phrase.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Alone each word is narrowing but together he is saying that this should almost never happen!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And if it does then you both should agree upon it.  It can\'92t be one of trying to be spiritual and saying you need to pray more.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Let me tell you what he is saying a different way\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Never stop having sex as a couple\'85except on very very very agreed upon mutual rare occasions.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And the only legitimate exception is prayer.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Then come together again so that Satan\'a0will not tempt you because of your lack of self-control.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to suggest something to you \'96 you need a guage!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I have a gas gauge in my car\'85it is so important because it tells me when I\'92m going to run out of gas!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I tell people in counseling they need to set up a gauge\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it doesn\'92t matter if they want to or not.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Somewhere we lost the purpose of sex and it turned into two things\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want to\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want kids\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Both have to do with desire\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ve forgotten the purpose of sex almost completely!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Direction determines destination\'85EVERY TIME!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you have stopped having sex or use it as a weapon or withhold for whatever reason, here is what you are doing.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Inviting Satan to come into you marriage and your bedroom.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I say this as a concession, not as a command.\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I wish that all of you were as I am.\'a0But each of you has your own gift from God; one has this gift, another has that.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Everyone has a different gift.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know some couples who have a spouse who really doesn\'92t matter too much if they have sex\'85maybe\'85maybe that is a gift.  I\'92m not too sure about that but maybe it is.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But if your spouse doesn\'92t have that gift you are leaving them on an island with no water.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Proverbs 5 says your spouse is like a fountain to drink from!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are some men and women here today who are dying of thirst, because one spouse doesn\'92t think it is a big deal or thinks it\'92s all about their desire and not their spouses.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f5\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 8\'a0
\f6\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Now to the unmarried
\fs15 \super [\ul a\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0and the widows I say: It is good for them to stay unmarried, as I do.\'a0
\f5\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f6\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But if they cannot control themselves, they should marry,\'a0for it is better to marry than to burn with passion.\
